## Sampling

Q.C. Department must draw the sample for analysis after the product is packed in the carton.

For Complete analysis	1 clinical carton

Control Samples		3 clinical cartons

Stability Samples		2 clinical cartons (once every quarter)

All packed goods must be kept in quarantine and released for dispatch only after Q.C. Department releases the batch.
